{"tid":216353,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel Coffee Lake 6核曝光, Core i5 6C6T","createTime":"2017-04-25T06:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T20:01:15.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90b6b42e88e46a5f4e8b3a2d2b2e59f73e6ce7d9","tid":216353,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>Intel Coffee Lake 6核曝光, Core i5 6C6T<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.coolaler.com/threads/intel-coffee-lake-6-core-i5-6c6t.344267/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Fintel-coffee-lake-6-core-i5-6c6t.344267%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d80658ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coolaler.com/threads/intel-coffee-lake-6-core-i5-6c6t.344267/</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\nIntel 預計在今年下半年推出第八代處理器，也就是 Coffee Lake，先前有傳言將會在8月提早報到，如果是真的，那第七代 Kaby Lake 真是超級過渡，另外 Coffee Lake 也將會首次在主流平台上下放6核心架構，這應該不是新聞了，最近在 Sisoftware 資料庫上出現了一顆6核心的 Core i5，應該就是 Coffee Lake。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/04/intel_coffee_lake_6c_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F04%2Fintel_coffee_lake_6c_1.png&h=27972fe9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n這款處理器是6C6T，核心時脈為3.5GHz，L2快取為6x256KB，L3快取9MB，Intel 在4核心的L3配置是8MB，所以6核心的配置應該會是12MB，當然這有可能是資料庫的識別錯誤，畢竟在未正式發布前是極有可能發生，但也有可能是針對 Core i5 的定位做閹割，畢竟是6C不支援HT，且得跟 Core i7 做出區隔才行。當然除了6C6T的 Core i5 應該也會有6C12T的 Core i7。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/04/intel_coffee_lake_6c_2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F04%2Fintel_coffee_lake_6c_2.png&h=a918280a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/04/intel_coffee_lake_6c_3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F04%2Fintel_coffee_lake_6c_3.png&h=65b22894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/04/intel_coffee_lake_6c_4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F04%2Fintel_coffee_lake_6c_4.png&h=6f77218d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nIntel Coffee Lake 將會搭配 300 系列晶片組，不過應該也可以相容於 200 系列，至於 100 系列就不確定了，這得看 Intel 要不要下放。"},{"pid":"bca853713e442448ee9e80e716c585bbcd15bdb0","tid":216353,"uid":142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"牙膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfb3c9d65ed9836e3a1da855356c1dc8318722e","tid":216353,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"expected"},{"pid":"e58d9638f1012fb60ab6d9f70ed6a2e5775d0ef9","tid":216353,"uid":37064,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:03:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ae0c1224698825fd54395839c3063732e462c88","tid":216353,"uid":55220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Coffee Lake<br />\n<br />\n咖啡腳</blockquote><br />\nlake 同foot 都唔識分 ,真係無撚言 好心你睇下書啦 仲上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d2ab22cc95917cf463cb22ddb6ae5a473b8e9c","tid":216353,"uid":90108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Coffee Lake<br />\n<br />\n咖啡腳</blockquote><br />\nlake 好似解湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\na粉路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc687ebc69dc6a0aab285548f240148d4ba00c15","tid":216353,"uid":69434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"平民6核來了<img src